72:The following phrases are frozen for release use until fixed or proven:
74:- "VERSE OS is formally verified" beyond the seL4 dependency.
75:- "formally proven" for VERSE user-space components.
76:- "self-healing" without the word "cooperative" and the exact TestWorker acceptance test.
77:- "scheduler enforcement" for DharmaNet.
78:- "TCB restart", "kernel restart", or "fresh process replacement".
79:- "cryptographic CodexFS" or "cryptographic storage integrity".
80:- "production-ready", "hardened", "impossible", or "guaranteed" for current implementation behavior.
